# Authentication System

The application uses Firebase Authentication for user management.

## Authentication Files
- [src/lib/firebase/config.ts](mdc:src/lib/firebase/config.ts) - Firebase configuration
- [src/lib/auth/AuthContext.tsx](mdc:src/lib/auth/AuthContext.tsx) - Authentication context provider
- [src/lib/auth/ProtectedRoute.tsx](mdc:src/lib/auth/ProtectedRoute.tsx) - Route protection component
- [src/pages/Auth/Login.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Auth/Login.tsx) - Login page
- [src/pages/Auth/Signup.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Auth/Signup.tsx) - Signup page
- [src/pages/Auth/ResetPassword.tsx](mdc:src/pages/Auth/ResetPassword.tsx) - Reset password page

## Authentication Features
- Email/Password Login
- Google Login
- Automatic Account Creation after successful payments
- ProtectedRoute component for securing routes

## Important Note
The `src/pages/Auth` directory is intentionally excluded from git tracking as it belongs to a separate repository. When developing locally, ensure the Auth files are properly copied to this location.
